title: Jewel -  Live at the Innerchange Coffe House in San Diego - 1994
description:
Please don't make me add the set list.  Two discs of songs.  There's a oouple of versions of some of the songs on her first album.  I'm not one to upload and newbie stuff of her's.  Any questions, comments or legal issues can be directed to the comments section of this post.  

More importantly:  these are soundboard quality tracks that did not make the Pieces of You record.  The nice young man at the Innerchange was kind enough to sacrifice these files for the greater good, though, sadly, for profit (WRONG!!).  Special thanks to the young man who was kind enough make this upload possible (no names, sorry, but you know who you are, and you will be duly notified.)

Alright, here's the set list after all (bloody typing on this. . .:

DISC 1:

1000 Miles Away
Who Will Save Your Soul
Sometimes It Be That Way
Boy Needs A Bike (Ride Away)
Fish Family
Daddy (NOT the song on Pieces Of You, though)
Communion (Later called: All The Animals)
Angel Needs A Ride
Nicotine Love
Painters
Circle Song
I'll Be Seeing You Again

DISC 2:

Pieces Of You
Who Will Save Your Soul (alternate version)
Chime Bells (Yodel Song)
Rocker Girl
She Cries
Never Mind
Hey, Mister
See Sassy
Swedish Song
Raven
Poem (not music - this is recited poetry - quite lovely, though)

Cheers and Enjoy!
